title: Comment from Volunteer Hobbs , STPS Fl ,WildLife, Harbor b ..

analysis.key_quote: Please do not have anymore launches please cap it, not only is this hurting our lagoon Sealife and fishing vessels but it is a security risk and a danger to all that live here.
analysis.rationale: The comment primarily addresses concerns about environmental impacts and safety related to rocket launches, without discussing civil service or the proposed rule. Therefore, it does not clearly support or oppose the rule.
